hews County, Virginia|Mathews County]]\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Mecklenburg County, Virginia|Mecklenburg County]]\n|8\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Montgomery County, Virginia|Montgomery County]]\n|6\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Nelson County, Virginia|Nelson County]]\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[New Kent County, Virginia|New Kent County]]\n|8\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Newport News, Virginia|Newport News (city)]]\n|48\n|1<ref name=\"Daily Press March 22\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Norfolk, Virginia|Norfolk (city)]]\n|55\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Northampton County, Virginia|Northampton County]]\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Northumberland County, Virginia|Northumberland County]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Nottoway County, Virginia|Nottoway County]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Orange County, Virginia|Orange County]]\n|5\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Page County, Virginia|Page County]]\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Peninsula Health District** \n|\n|1<ref name=\"WTVR-March22\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Petersburg, Virginia|Petersburg (city)]]\n|10\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Pittsylvania County, Virginia|Pittsylvania County]]\n|2\n|1<ref>{{cite web |last1=Palmer |first1=Ewan |title=Virginia pastor dies from coronavirus after previously saying \"media is pumping out fear\" about pandemic |url=https://www.newsweek.com/virginia-pastor-dies-coronavirus-after-previously-saying-media-pumping-out-fear-about-pandemic-1494702 |website=Newsweek |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329100924/https://www.newsweek.com/virginia-pastor-dies-coronavirus-after-previously-saying-media-pumping-out-fear-about-pandemic-1494702 |archivedate=29 March 2020 |language=en |date=27 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hand |first1=Mark |title=VA Pastor, Musician Dies Fr